    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Species of South American evergreen shrub and tree of the holly family, having leaves that are used for an infusion beverage that is high in caffeine content.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
